                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="endfooter">
                <div class="container">
                    <p>© 2025 <b>Cheese Cheese</b>. All rights reserved.</p>
                    <p class="credit">Designed with <i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i> by <b>Hau Nguyen</b> and <b>Thao Le</b></p>
